@prefix :    <https://civic-data.de/pipeline#> .
@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .

# Curated match knowledge for the example. Empty — the two sources match on
# postal code + fuzzy name alone. This is where hand-curated overrides go:
#
#   :cityopen-co-3 owl:sameAs       :civichub-ch-102 .   # force into one cluster
#   :cityopen-co-3 owl:differentFrom :civichub-ch-104 .  # veto a merge, never cluster
#
# owl:sameAs forces two records together regardless of score; owl:differentFrom
# pins two apart even when they clear the match rule.
